@title The Flexible Config System
@doc

<p> This provides a really simple and straitforward means of provide a
nice heirarchical config mechinism for erlang otp based systems.  </p>

<p>
The system provides for making heirarchical queries into the config system. The api for these queries are defined in the fconf module.

Generally queries can be in the form "some.path.to.thing"

</p>

